This is a features files.

This file wil contain all the ideas I have prepared to implement in the project.

Base Features
=============

The project will be to create a Universal Profile System where the code can later be modified to be implemented into anytype of system.
In today's world there is a login/logout user account system for anytypes of business. This Universal Profile System will help other
developer to easy jump start without any difficulties. Save time and coffee money.


Features to be implemented
==========================

# Create a login system with SHA1 password encryption.
# Use Single Sign Login Authentication (Facebook, Twitter etc).
# User can upload profile photo, update their profile details and update status.
# more to come... 
